Package: ordgam
Type: Package
Title: Additive Proportional Odds Model for Ordinal Data using Laplace Approximations and Bayesian P-Splines
Version: 0.9.0
Authors@R: person("Philippe","Lambert", 
 email="p.lambert@uliege.be", role=c("aut","cre"),
 comment=c(ORCID ="0000-0002-3670-3328"))
Maintainer: Philippe Lambert <p.lambert@uliege.be>
BugReports: https://github.com/plambertULiege/ordgam/issues
Description: Additive proportional odds model for ordinal data using Bayesian P-splines. The combination of Laplace approximations and of P-splines enable fast and flexible inference in a Bayesian framework. For more details, see Lambert and Gressani (Statistical Modelling, 2023 ; Preprint: <arXiv:2210.01668>).
